<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include('./partials/head') %>
  <title>About Us</title>
  <style>
    .about-header {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .about-section {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 3rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .about-content {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: rgb(250, 133, 90);
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .team-section {
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .team-header {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .team-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .team-card img {
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .team-card h5 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .team-card p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('./partials/nav') %>

  <div class="container" style="margin-top: 70px;">
    <!-- About Us Header -->
    <h1 class="about-header">About Us</h1>

    <!-- About Us Content -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <p class="about-content">
        Welcome to <span class="highlight">Our Platform</span>, where innovation meets opportunity. Founded with a mission to bridge gaps and connect people, 
        our platform is dedicated to empowering individuals and organizations alike. Whether you are seeking career growth, business partnerships, or community 
        engagement, we are here to support you every step of the way.
      </p>

      <p class="about-content mt-3">
        With years of expertise and a passion for creating meaningful solutions, our team has developed a space that fosters collaboration and inspires success. 
        Our values are rooted in <span class="highlight">integrity</span>, <span class="highlight">innovation</span>, and <span class="highlight">inclusion</span>. 
        These principles guide every decision we make and every service we provide.
      </p>

      <p class="about-content mt-3">
        We take pride in offering a diverse range of features tailored to meet your needs, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="about-content">
        <li>Comprehensive job portals to help individuals and companies find their perfect match.</li>
        <li>Networking tools to build meaningful connections within your industry.</li>
        <li>Resources for skill development, mentorship, and community impact.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="about-content mt-3">
        As we look to the future, we remain committed to expanding our services and driving positive change. Join us on this journey, and let's achieve greatness together.
      </p>
    </div>


  <%- include('./partials/scripts') %>
</body>

</html>
